The paper deals with generating questions to disambiguate visual instances, which suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also introduces a new dataset and an effective method for question generation, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
